{"search_data": "Uttar PradeshNIDHI EIR Yojana Launched in Uttar Pradesh for Engineering StudentsNIDHI EIR Yojana for Engineering StudentThis scheme is providing monetary incentives to meritorious students of engineering colleges for one year. Under the scheme, the state government will offer of Rs. 20,000 to Rs. 30,000 per month for one year to engineering students based on excellency of their ideas.Moreover, under NIDHI EIR Yojana, the government will provide loan facilities (collateral free loan) to those students who wants to set up their own business based of their developed engineering project. However, their project should have been able to adapt to the changing times and supply the needs of communities throughout the country.NIDHI is an umbrella program conceived and developed by the Innovation & Entrepreneurship division, Department of Science & Technology, Government of India, for nurturing ideas and innovations (knowledge-based and technology-driven) into successful startups.TO get more information about this scheme visit on official website at www.nidhi-eir.in or click this link  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}